        h2 Disc Brake <span class="tilt-l">Seminar</span>
      div(class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8")      
        p In this seminar we will go over both mechanical and hydraulic disc brake systems in detail
        p Topics include
        ul(class="list--indented")
          li General Maintenance and Upkeep
          li Pad Replacement
          li Rotor Replacement
          li Caliper Adjustment
          li Hydraulic Brake Bleed
          
